title: Carly Aquilino: Trashy Christmas
description: Carly Aquilino joins us to talk trashy Christmas, growing up on Long Island, and crappy stores at the mall. You may know Carly Aquilino from MTV Girl Code, Guy Code, performing stand up comedy all over the country, and her podcast Secret Keepers Club. Subscribe. Rate. Review.
